These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, spanish, australian, french
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, jazz, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the australian##1
2. the french is on the right of the nigerian##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the chinese is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the nigerian is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish | nigerian | french | australian |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep | jazz     | pop       | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, mauve, blood-red, blue, turquise
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the person who likes turquise is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta | almond-milk | soy-milk | sprite |
| Color   | blood-red  | blue   | lilac       | mauve    | turquise   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There 5 different types of food: apricot, garlic, kale, nectarine, raspberry
There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, white, aquamarine, yellow, fuchsia
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
4. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person eating garlic is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food        | kale | nectarine | garlic | apricot | raspberry |
| Color   | white  | emerald      | fuchsia | aquamarine | yellow      |

