.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, fishing, reading, sudoku, traveling
There are 5 different nationalities: british, turkish, colombian, egyptian, brazilian
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the british##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the colombian is on the far right##1
7. the brazilian is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | sudoku    | baking        | reading | fishing | traveling |
| Nationality     | british | egyptian | brazilian  | turkish   | colombian |

