.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
5 different games are played: poker, canasta, whist, mah-jongg, monopoly
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person playing canasta is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the person playing monopoly is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Game   | poker | mah-jongg | whist | monopoly | canasta     |

