.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, handball, volleyball
House: ranch-style, cottage, palace, cape-cod, wooden
1. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
3. the palace house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the palace house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | handball   | cricket   | baseball | volleyball | badminton |
| House   | cottage | palace | cape-cod   | wooden | ranch-style       |

