.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
House: ranch-style, palace, wooden, townhouse, colonial
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, rugby, tennis, water-polo
1. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the ranch-style house##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| House     | palace   | wooden  | colonial      | ranch-style | townhouse     |
| Sport   | tennis | rugby | biathlon | baseball   | water-polo |

