.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, marigold, rose, amaryllis, begonia
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Flower     | marigold | azalea       | begonia | amaryllis | rose    |
| Sport   | tennis   | water-polo | soccer  | rugby     | ice-hockey |

