.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  librarian, writer, scientist, software-developer, engineer
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, classical, house, indie, rock
1. the fan of house is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the scientist is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the writer is on the far right##1
4. the software-developer is on the far left##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the engineer is the fan of classical##1
7. the software-developer is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian | scientist | engineer | writer |
| Music-Genre   | house       | indie   | rock         | classical   | blues   |

