.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There 5 different types of food: apple, artichoke, avocado, cherry, pomegranate
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, chess, scrabble, canasta
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing billiard is the person eating cherry##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person playing canasta is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | cherry | apple  | avocado | artichoke | pomegranate |
| Game    | billiard    | scrabble | canasta   | mah-jongg       | chess        |

