.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There are 5 different nationalities: british, german, malaysian, nigerian, italian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse, surfing, weightlifting
1. the italian is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the nigerian is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the italian is on the left of the german##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the german##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Nationality    | british | nigerian          | malaysian    | italian | german  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | biathlon | surfing | cricket |

