.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, ebony, mauve, turquise, lilac
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, train, tram
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes lilac is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the person who likes turquise is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Color   | mauve | chestnut      | turquise | ebony | lilac |
| Transport     | train  | snowmobile | bus     | tram     | subway  |

