.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, sprite
5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, domino, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | sprite | hot-chocolate | cola      | soy-milk | fanta      |
| Game   | mah-jongg  | scrabble       | backgammon | monopoly  | domino |

