.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, nurse, pilot, software-developer
City: edinburgh, marseilles, colone, boston, rome
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the software-developer is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the person traveling to colone is the nurse##1
5. the engineer is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the nurse##1
7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Job           | pilot     | software-developer | accountant | nurse  | engineer |
| City   | edinburgh | rome               | marseilles     | colone | boston |

