.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-16::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, skateboarding, baseball, biathlon
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, dancing, filmmaking, photography, woodworking
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| Sport    | soccer   | skateboarding | biathlon      | lacrosse | baseball        |
| Hobby   | woodworking | chess     | filmmaking | dancing | photography |

