.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, sports, time-travel
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, green, apricot, black
1. the person who likes apricot is in the middle##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who likes black##1
5. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes green##1
7. the person who likes black is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | sports  | action | time-travel | romance  |
| Color         | blood-red | green | apricot  | black    | ebony |

